{"tid":1624844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(香城online) 各位火魔法師同我聽住！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:34:07.000Z","uid":61060,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad9facc36f1b44de2065ac00f956cbdea62474d","tid":1624844,"uid":61060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"雞尾酒扔狗車好過用黎扔狗，一黎d狗衫防火，傷害有限，二黎燒狗車可以大幅削弱狗狗既機動性。D狗無哂機動性就可以轉場玩！而佢地只可以on99 call車黎接佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試諗下d狗個個full gear, 狗車著哂火，無車接載走得幾遠？分分鐘連狗屋都翻唔到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，建議雞尾酒扔車頭冚，一黎因為d機器起哂車頭冚下面，燒著d機器就玩完。二黎車頭冚著火，司機睇唔到路，如果開車d火更加會向司機位燒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"b092159f16cf1963870a7a7275f39b9f66438374","tid":1624844,"uid":61060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca799fffd147e8e2553ed7dad356c1d806477ef2","tid":1624844,"uid":61060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:09:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d4e647f2ac6c2ad5a549dfd967a1f4a0a1f44a4","tid":1624844,"uid":61060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:22:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d122adf90a338f6fa86f53a75c0c849d5eb5451c","tid":1624844,"uid":273188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"(經濟抗爭)橫掂港元儲蓄都無利息，應該轉錢去current account<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624948</a>"},{"pid":"6eab536575401e3ac9dc83eeca0edd8df47af077","tid":1624844,"uid":61060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a5f9b4af6e731b018570015288f417e99a7040b","tid":1624844,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmo